| Pattern | Example | Notes |
|---------|---------|-------|
| **Image-only** | ImageClassificationPipeline | processor only |
| **Text-only** | TextClassificationPipeline | tokenizer only |
| **Image→Text (generation)** | ImageToTextPipeline | processor + tokenizer + model.generate() |
