| **Audio+Text (joint)** | ZeroShotAudioClassificationPipeline | processor, tokenizer, model({ ...text_inputs, ...audio_inputs }) |
| **Batching** | All multimodal | Check `Array.isArray()` at start, return batched if input was batched |

